Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加速…了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是3D影像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.78,0:00:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.06,0:00:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙一副吓得腿软的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对他的名字也没印象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.01,0:00:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他是金属色  多少有点能耐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是NPC而是人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是超频连线者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(330,328)}Burst  Linker
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.18,0:00:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是久违的世纪末场地  Lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:01:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手还是个亮闪闪的菜鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超幸运的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  你却是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒大霉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.92,0:01:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该不会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢得了就有鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.18,0:01:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就被人逮到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.71,0:01:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差点以为自己要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.71,0:01:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为你没履行好和我的约定  少年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一不留神接上全球网络是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就可以省下口头说明了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.66,0:01:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你已经发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.02,0:01:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Brain  Burst这款程序是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一款单纯的对战格斗游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:02:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是以现实世界为舞台的遭遇战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.61,0:02:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:04.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真够夸张的
